      "content": "idk i'm kinda worried a doctor might just tell me to drink more water and charge me like 50 euros for nothing lol. it was just so sudden, like i was fine and then boom. if i take a decent amount of ibuprofen and some melatonin to sleep, do you think that'll help clear the fog by morning? i have a big exam tomorrow and really cant miss it.",
