      "content": "yea i get that but im a bit nauseous too now. like i don't want to go to the er for something that might just be stress or thirst. if i just take a double dose of ibuprofen and maybe some extra melatonin to really knock me out so i dont have to think about it, would that be a safe way to just reset my system for tomorrow? i just need to sleep through this fog.",
